        <p>
          This website is provided for the purpose of sharing information about Alnmouth Village Golf Club, enabling visitor bookings, facilitating member access to club services, and processing payments. You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Membership</h2>
        <p>
          Membership of Alnmouth Village Golf Club is subject to the club's constitution and rules. Annual subscriptions are due as set out by the club committee. Members are expected to comply with the club's rules, dress code, and etiquette standards at all times.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Visitor Green Fees</h2>
        <p>
          Green fee prices are as displayed on our website and are subject to change. Booking is recommended and can be made through BRS Golf. All visitors must check in at the clubhouse before play.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Online Payments</h2>
        <p>
          Online payments are processed securely by DOJO (Paymentsense Ltd.). By making a payment through our website, you agree to DOJO's terms of service. All prices are displayed in pounds sterling (GBP) and include VAT where applicable.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you make a payment, you will be redirected to DOJO's secure checkout page. Your payment card details are processed entirely by DOJO and are never stored on our systems. We accept Visa, Mastercard, and American Express.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Refund Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Please see our separate <a href="/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a> page for full details on refunds and cancellations.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>
