          All content on this website, including text, images, logos, and design, is the property of Alnmouth Village Golf Club Ltd. and is protected by copyright. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any content without our prior written permission.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          While we make every effort to ensure the information on this website is accurate and up to date, we make no warranties or guarantees about its completeness or accuracy. Alnmouth Village Golf Club Ltd. shall not be liable for any loss or damage arising from the use of this website.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your use of this website is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>, which explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Links to Third-Party Websites</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites (such as BRS Golf for bookings). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these external sites.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update these Terms &amp; Conditions at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of any changes.
        </p>

        <h2>12. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms &amp; Conditions are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
        </p>

        <h2>13. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about these Terms &amp; Conditions, please contact:
        </p>
        <p>
          Alnmouth Village Golf Club Ltd.<br>
          Marine Road, Alnmouth<br>
          Northumberland NE66 2RZ<br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:Manager@AlnmouthVillage.Golf">Manager@AlnmouthVillage.Golf</a><br>
          Phone: <a href="tel:01665830370">01665 830370</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .policy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .policy-updated {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .policy-container h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .policy-container p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .policy-container ul {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .policy-container li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .policy-container a {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
  </style>
</PublicLayout>
